00:00:26,758 --> 00:00:30,819
un dos iz geven a teyl fun ale polyakn, azoy hobn zey gefilt vegn dem.

9
00:00:31,220 --> 00:00:32,060
ober

10
00:00:32,950 --> 00:00:38,464
tragish iz geven ven ikh hob get- ikh hob getrofn a bokher vos iz geven alt eyn un tsvantsik yor,

11
00:00:38,605 --> 00:00:41,147
a raykher zindl fun a dokter,

12
00:00:41,338 --> 00:00:43,677
un er hot zikh oysgebahaltn

13
00:00:44,072 --> 00:00:45,753
bay di polyakn.

14
00:00:46,317 --> 00:00:50,847
dos iz geven bar a dinst bay velkhe a, hot gearbet bay zayn tatn mit der mamen,

15
00:00:50,847 --> 00:00:53,450
hot men mistam batsolt a groyse sume gelt,

16
00:00:53,505 --> 00:00:57,026
un zey hobn im oysgegaltn di gantse tsvey yor tsayt

17
00:00:57,825 --> 00:00:59,079
nokhn geto,

18
00:00:59,079 --> 00:01:01,160
tsi in meshekh fun geto.

19
00:01:01,437 --> 00:01:03,644
shpeter, in eyn tog,

20
00:01:03,644 --> 00:01:06,150
nokh der bafrayung, vi ikh zog, &lt;in&gt; Byalistok

21
00:01:06,150 --> 00:01:09,210
zaynen arayn a &lt;kovtse&gt;, s'iz geven a organizatsye,

22
00:01:09,679 --> 00:01:10,489
polyakn,

23
00:01:10,554 --> 00:01:12,331
m'hot aroysgenumen dem bokher,

24
00:01:12,658 --> 00:01:14,359
m'hot im avekgezetst

25
00:01:14,359 --> 00:01:18,288
oyf di trep un m'hot im arayngevorfn a koyl in kop un m'hot im derharget.

26
00:01:18,835 --> 00:01:21,444
di zakhn vos iz geblibn mit mir,

27
00:01:21,535 --> 00:01:24,687
un ikh ken es nisht fargesn, az nokh der milkhome,

28
00:01:24,687 --> 00:01:26,034
nokh dem

29
00:01:26,682 --> 00:01:29,443
vi mir hobn shoyn ibergelebt dem gehenem,

30
00:01:29,685 --> 00:01:33,459
zaynen nokh di polyakn geven gut tsu undz. zey hobn nokh geharget.

31
00:01:33,921 --> 00:01:36,513
bay undz flegt geyn a ban fun Varshe

32
00:01:39,118 --> 00:01:43,702
d- keyn Byalistok, fun Varshe, un oyfn mitn veg iz geven Lape, aza shtetl.

33
00:01:43,708 --> 00:01:46,182
dortn flegt men opvartn di banen,

34
00:01:46,392 --> 00:01:50,098
aropnemen di yidn, oysklaybn di yidn fun dem tsug,

35
00:01:50,914 --> 00:01:53,777
un oyston naket,

36
00:01:54,154 --> 00:01:55,801
oder derhargenen,

37
00:01:55,825 --> 00:01:58,910
oder dir lozn shteyn oyfn veg in gantsn a naketer.

38
00:01:58,910 --> 00:02:01,050
zey hobn oyfgeton shreklekhe zakhn.

39
00:02:02,102 --> 00:02:05,268
du farshteyst? s'iz shver haynt tsu tog,

40
00:02:05,882 --> 00:02:07,800
ven ir redt vegn Poyln,

41
00:02:09,814 --> 00:02:13,084
nisht vos ikh bin biter. m'ken a gantsn folk nisht...

42
00:02:13,084 --> 00:02:16,035
di daytshn bashuldik ikh dos folk. vegn di polyakn

43
00:02:16,108 --> 00:02:18,582
hob ikh nisht keyn gut vort oykh far zey.

44
00:02:19,551 --> 00:02:23,291
zaynen geven zeyer zeyer gr-, az, zey hobn gekent bavayzn...

45
00:02:23,567 --> 00:02:29,535
farshteyst? mayn man lernt mikh az ikh tor nit bashuldikn alts. er vil, er zukht yoysher un gerekhtikeyt,

46
00:02:29,659 --> 00:02:31,863
ober mit mayne erfarungen,

47
00:02:31,988 --> 00:02:33,768
du zest? ikh farentfer zikh mamesh

48
00:02:33,768 --> 00:02:37,488
far vos ikh fil azoy. ober ikh hob gegat bavayzn, shvarts oyf vays,

49
00:02:37,488 --> 00:02:40,402
zaynen nisht geven gut tsu undz, zaynen nisht geven.

50
00:02:41,539 --> 00:02:44,430
un oybe s'iz do geratevete yidn fun Poyln

51
00:02:44,430 --> 00:02:46,067
fu- durkh polyakn,

52
00:02:46,067 --> 00:02:48,083
hobn es geton far a sakh gelt.

53
00:02:48,083 --> 00:02:50,176
zey hobn, emes, zey hobn ayngeshtelt zeyer lebn.

54
00:02:50,176 --> 00:02:51,489
dos iz emes.

55
00:02:51,630 --> 00:02:56,006
un dos iz a zakh vos iz nisht geshen yetst mistame. dos iz doyres doyres

56
00:02:56,006 --> 00:02:57,415
zikh ongezamlt,

57
00:02:57,415 --> 00:03:00,939
ober keyn libe tsvishn yidn mit polyakn iz es keyn mol nisht geven.

58
00:03:02,565 --> 00:03:06,575
du host mir dertseylt ah vegn dayn tokhter vos iz geboyrn in STOCKHOLM.

59
00:03:06,261 --> 00:03:07,098
ye.

60
00:03:06,771 --> 00:03:07,207
yo.

