66
00:03:14,740 --> 00:03:15,890
zi iz ge-

67
00:03:16,183 --> 00:03:17,426
zi iz geboyrn ven?

68
00:03:17,331 --> 00:03:21,932
zi iz geborn gevorn dem fertn yanuar nayntsn akht un fertsik in Shtokholm.

69
00:03:21,955 --> 00:03:22,742
ye.

70
00:03:23,372 --> 00:03:27,365
un Soren hobn mir gebrakht do ven zi iz alt geven a yor.

71
00:03:28,283 --> 00:03:32,377
un Sore, dos ershte vos, mit vos ikh bin zeyer shtolts,

72
00:03:32,620 --> 00:03:37,423
ikh hob ale mol gezogt, ikh hob nisht gegat keyn bildung; mayne kinder muzn hobn.

73
00:03:37,615 --> 00:03:42,252
hot gemakht eyn MASTER'S DEGREE un a tsveytn MASTER'S DEGREE, a MASTER in

74
00:03:42,252 --> 00:03:45,540
englishe literatur, un a MASTER in SOCIAL WORK,

75
00:03:45,715 --> 00:03:48,054
un zi iz a fayner mentsh.

76
00:03:48,162 --> 00:03:52,341
ir ershte shprakh iz oykh yidish, mit vos mir zaynen zeyer shtolts,

77
00:03:53,393 --> 00:03:55,125
un ir hot oykh a zun, yo?

78
00:03:54,456 --> 00:03:58,314
ikh hob a zun vos iz a lerer, er iz oykh in Toronto.

79
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,326
vi heyst er?

80
00:03:59,029 --> 00:04:01,436
er er heyst heyst Hershl Fayner.

81
00:04:01,358 --> 00:04:02,567
un geboyrn?

82
00:04:02,083 --> 00:04:06,177
geboyrn gevorn iz er in nayntsn eyn un fuftsik in Toronto,

83
00:04:07,045 --> 00:04:10,560
un a fayner mentsh, a yidish-rednder bokher,

84
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:13,772
vos ikh bin zeyer shtolts, un er iz a tate fun tsvey kinder.

85
00:04:14,571 --> 00:04:16,759
un vi heyst zayn vayb?

86
00:04:16,630 --> 00:04:18,514
zayn vayb heyst FRANNY,

87
00:04:18,672 --> 00:04:19,543
ye.

88
00:04:19,767 --> 00:04:22,631
un di kinder, s'iz dortn do a AVRA,

89
00:04:22,519 --> 00:04:23,525
AVRA.

90
00:04:23,397 --> 00:04:24,808
un LEWIS.

91
00:04:24,291 --> 00:04:25,989
un LEWIS, yo.

92
00:04:24,949 --> 00:04:25,916
ye.

93
00:04:25,916 --> 00:04:28,301
un mayn tokhter hot tsvey kinder.

94
00:04:28,645 --> 00:04:30,242
s'iz do ARIADNE,

95
00:04:29,944 --> 00:04:31,203
ARIADNE.

96
00:04:30,636 --> 00:04:32,520
YES un

