ye.

103
00:04:37,892 --> 00:04:43,657
AND mit vos hot, hostu zikh basheftikt do in Toronto zint du bist gekumen?

104
00:04:43,107 --> 00:04:49,111
ikh hob nisht gearbet. ikh bin geven a mame tsu mayne kinder. ikh bin aktiv in, gezelshaftlekh, in Arbeter-Ring,

105
00:04:49,111 --> 00:04:54,862
un mayn man iz geven der parnose-geber. er iz a bukhhalter fun fakh un er hot gegarbet do.

106
00:04:54,970 --> 00:05:01,764
di ershte yorn hot er gegangen in shules. er hot genumen a shtikl tsayt biz er iz avek arbetn, vayl er iz geven a bukhhalter nokh frier.

107
00:05:01,888 --> 00:05:09,948
un er hot in der heym gehat hekhere bildung, azoyernokh az &lt;s'iz&gt;, er hot nisht gehat keyn problem nisht mit der shprakh un nisht mitn oyslernen zikh di fa- tsurikgeyn.

108
00:05:10,174 --> 00:05:12,986
MISSUS Fayner, tsum sof vil ikh dir fregn,

109
00:05:12,267 --> 00:05:13,189
fregn, bite.

110
00:05:13,532 --> 00:05:15,854
vos darf di velt zikh oyslernen

111
00:05:16,030 --> 00:05:17,694
fun di ale derfarungen?

112
00:05:17,211 --> 00:05:22,065
mayn tayerer. di velt hot nisht gelernt, ikh gloyb nit az zi vet epes lernen.

113
00:05:22,965 --> 00:05:26,891
der respekt farn mentshlekhn lebn, farn mentsh vi a mentsh.

114
00:05:27,100 --> 00:05:27,974
vi ken,

115
00:05:27,974 --> 00:05:33,542
az me ken haynt tsu tog zayn in a Bosnye, un s'ken haynt tsu tog zayn in andere lender vu men harget un men shlogt,

116
00:05:33,542 --> 00:05:35,598
di velt hot nisht gelernt fun dem.

117
00:05:35,993 --> 00:05:39,651
un vifl iz do antisemitn haynt tsu tog velkhe hasn yidn?

118
00:05:39,651 --> 00:05:40,377
vos,

119
00:05:40,377 --> 00:05:42,821
m'hot umgebrakht zeks milyon yidn!

120
00:05:43,553 --> 00:05:47,617
un a velt hot geshvign in yener tsayt, un haynt tsu tog,

121
00:05:47,617 --> 00:05:51,512
nokh aza min kurtse tsayt, vos iz fuftsik yor far der geshikhte?

122
00:05:51,872 --> 00:05:53,303
es kumen tsu geyn

123
00:05:53,303 --> 00:05:57,941
un s'iz do antisemitishe grupes, s'iz do Natsi-grupes, s'iz do farsheydene, un Daytshland,

124
00:05:58,183 --> 00:06:00,492
Daytshland vi aza vos hot gedarft di ersht-

125
00:06:00,492 --> 00:06:06,041
zi hot gegat di ergste mapole, un zi hot haynt oyfgevoksn, zi iz gevorn groys, zi iz gevorn mekhtik un zey hobn,

126
00:06:06,418 --> 00:06:11,221
zey hobn, di SKINHEADS, vos hobn zey nisht dortn? shreklekhe zakhn vos kumen for.

127
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:16,369
oyfhaltn yidishkeyt iz bay dir vikhtik? Yisroel iz dir vikhtik?

128
00:06:15,953 --> 00:06:19,670
far mir iz vikhtik di yidishe shprakh vi aza,

129
00:06:19,670 --> 00:06:21,467
vayl mayn mishpokhe

130
00:06:21,467 --> 00:06:23,540
iz umgekumen mit yidish oyf di lipn.

131
00:06:24,627 --> 00:06:26,173
Yisroel iz a,

132
00:06:26,297 --> 00:06:29,244
ikh, nisht derfar vayl ikh bin a tsienistke,

133
00:06:29,250 --> 00:06:33,226
nor Yisroel iz a plats vu es lebn finf milyon yidn,

134
00:06:33,604 --> 00:06:34,863
tsi nokh mer.

135
00:06:34,903 --> 00:06:37,107
yeder yid iz far mir a oytser,

136
00:06:37,738 --> 00:06:39,583
un far, fa-, vel ikh alts ton.

137
00:06:39,583 --> 00:06:44,561
oybe s'iz ophengik in mir epes tsu ton tsu helfn Yisroel bin ikh do de-, bin ikh derfar, ABSOLUTELY.

138
00:06:44,561 --> 00:06:46,574
zeyer vikhtik far mir, Yisroel.

139
00:06:47,070 --> 00:06:49,291
un yeder yid iz far mir vikhtik.

140
00:06:50,631 --> 00:06:52,835
un oyfhaltn yidishkeyt iz vikhtik?

141
00:06:52,808 --> 00:06:55,302
mayn yidishkeyt oyf mayn shteyger.

142
00:06:55,302 --> 00:06:56,413
du farshteyst?

143
00:06:57,651 --> 00:07:02,825
mayn yidishkeyt, di yidishkeyt mayne bashteyt in der shprakh, yidishe shprakh, yidishe literatur,

144
00:07:02,950 --> 00:07:06,758
yidishe geshikhte vos ikh hob gegebn mayne kinder ertsoygn azoy,

145
00:07:07,050 --> 00:07:10,419
un ikh veys nit tsi s'vet meglekh zayn mit mayne eyniklekh.

146
00:07:10,982 --> 00:07:13,541
ober ikh tu es vi vayt s'iz meglekh,

147
00:07:13,986 --> 00:07:18,283
un ikh arbet in a organizatsye vos shtitst alts vos iz yidish, ye?

148
00:07:18,745 --> 00:07:20,986
un ikh, vi ikh hob gezogt frier,

149
00:07:20,986 --> 00:07:26,771
ikh hob respekt far yedn yid vos gloybt, tsi er gloybt nit, az er iz a yid un firt zikh oyf vi a yid,

150
00:07:27,553 --> 00:07:30,010
iz er mir noent tsum harts, vayl er iz a yid.

151
00:07:30,473 --> 00:07:32,782
MISSUS Fayner, ikh dank aykh zeyer.

152
00:07:33,402 --> 00:07:34,385
a dank.

153
00:07:39,950 --> 00:07:43,470
der bild iz genumen gevorn in Toronto,

154
00:07:43,939 --> 00:07:46,903
vayl mayn tokhter iz gekumen fun Grikhnland.

155
00:07:47,213 --> 00:07:49,417
do iz faran der ershter

156
00:07:50,149 --> 00:07:52,320
iz mayn zun HARVEY,

157
00:07:53,608 --> 00:07:56,555
un dos tsveyte iz mayn shnur FRANNY,

158
00:07:57,540 --> 00:07:59,123
un dos drite

159
00:07:59,123 --> 00:08:01,567
iz mayn tokhter Sorele.

160
00:08:02,839 --> 00:08:07,136
fun der zayt lebn Arn... lebn Hershlen,

161
00:08:07,294 --> 00:08:09,110
shteyt ARIADNE

162
00:08:10,332 --> 00:08:11,476
un Leon,

163
00:08:11,476 --> 00:08:14,240
mayn tsveyter eynikl, un dan

164
00:08:14,702 --> 00:08:17,750
zeyer tekhterl AVRA.

165
00:08:22,701 --> 00:08:28,753
dos iz a bild fun mayne beyde eyniklekh velkhe hobn gevoynt biz yetst in Grikhnland.

166
00:08:29,282 --> 00:08:30,966
dos iz ARIADNE

167
00:08:30,966 --> 00:08:31,976
un Leon.

168
00:08:32,015 --> 00:08:35,502
gemakht gevorn in Grikhnland in shule bay zey.

169
00:08:39,171 --> 00:08:40,920
un dos iz a bild

170
00:08:41,061 --> 00:08:45,155
fun mayn zun's tekhterl AVRA.

171
00:08:46,512 --> 00:08:49,121
zi iz n- haynt nayn yor alt.

172
00:08:52,789 --> 00:08:58,251
un dos iz mayn zun's zinele Leybele,

173
00:08:58,324 --> 00:09:03,270
